quran[8]{c,v,t,f}:
  25,76,"Olúṣegbére ni wọ́n nínú rẹ̀. Ó dára ní ibùgbé àti ibùdúró."
  25,77,"Sọ pé: “Olúwa mi kò kà yín kún tí kì í bá ṣe àdúà yín (àti ìjọ́sìn yín). Ẹ kúkú ti pe (àwọn āyah Rẹ̀) nírọ́. Láìpẹ́ ó sì máa di ìyà àìnípẹ̀kun (fún yín).”"
  26,49,"Fir‘aon wí pé: “Ẹ gbà Á gbọ́ ṣíwájú kí n̄g tó yọ̀ǹda fún yín! Dájúdájú òun ni àgbà yín tí ó kọ yín ní idán pípa. Láìpẹ́ ẹ̀ ń bọ̀ wá mọ̀. Dájúdájú mo máa gé ọwọ́ yín àti ẹsẹ̀ yín ní ìpasípayọ. Lẹ́yìn náà, dájúdájú mo máa kan gbogbo yín mọ́gi.”"
  26,50,"(Àwọn òpìdán) sọ pé: “Kò sí ìnira fún wa! Dájúdájú àwa yó sì fàbọ̀ sí ọ̀dọ̀ Olúwa wa."
  26,51,"Dájúdájú àwa n retí pé Olúwa wa yóò ṣe àforíjìn àwọn àṣìṣe wa fún wa nítorí pé àwa jẹ́ ẹni àkọ́kọ́ (tí ó jẹ́) onígbàgbọ́ òdodo.”{1}.",1:[Ìyẹn ni pé, wọ́n jẹ́ ẹni àkọ́kọ́ tó gba Allāhu gbọ́ nínú ìjọ Fir‘aon. Kì í ṣe pé wọ́n jẹ́ ẹni àkọ́kọ tó gba Allāhu gbọ́ nínú àwọn ènìyàn.]
  27,22,"(Ànábì Sulaemọ̄n) kò dúró pẹ́ (títí ó fi dé), ó sì wí pé: “Mo mọ n̄ǹkan tí o ò mọ̀. Mo sì mú ìró kan tó dájú wá bá ọ láti ìlú Saba’i."
  27,23,"Dájúdájú èmi bá obìnrin kan (ní ìlú Saba’i), tó ń jọba lé wọn lórí. Wọ́n fún un ní gbogbo n̄ǹkan. Ó sì ní ìtẹ́ ńlá kan."
  27,24,"Mo sì bá òun àti àwọn ènìyàn rẹ̀ tí wọ́n ń forí kanlẹ̀ fún òòrùn lẹ́yìn Allāhu. Aṣ-ṣaetọ̄n sì ṣe àwọn iṣẹ́ wọn ní ọ̀ṣọ́ fún wọn. Ó ṣẹ́rí wọn kúrò lójú ọ̀nà (òdodo). Nítorí náà, wọn kò sì mọ̀nà."